{"rule_id": "d87e48d6-80ea-4657-9a5c-0d5339b1bf9e", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "服务质量取消率计算方式", "summary": "取消百分比基于过去14天（不含当天）卖家过错导致的取消除以总发货量，涉及的违规行为包括库存过时、拣货发货问题、发货严重延迟等。", "content": "- 计算周期：过去14天，不包括计算当天\n- 公式：卖家过错取消数 ÷ 总发货量\n- 被认定为卖家过错的取消包括：卖家后台手动取消、因发货延迟7天由Ozon自动取消\n- 违规行为：仓库库存过时、拣货/发货问题、发货方式错误、第三方物流因卖家过错取消、严重发货延迟\n- 若超额系统会在账户中通知", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/ratings/quality-metrics?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["metric calculation", "cancellation rate", "service quality"]}
{"rule_id": "39192247-308a-4af2-84b4-9d2076641362", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "添加链接到其他平台以改善价格指数", "summary": "卖家可手动添加产品在其他市场平台的链接，帮助Ozon更准确计算价格指数。添加后72小时内更新到产品详情页。", "content": "- 在'价格与促销 → 管理价格'页面，点击价格值。\n- 在'价格指数'区域，点击'添加链接'。\n- 粘贴产品在其他市场平台的链接，可添加多个。\n- 点击'发送'进行验证。\n- 新数据将在72小时内显示在产品详情页。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/ratings/price-index?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["价格指数", "添加链接", "竞争对比"]}
{"rule_id": "1c4c4ba6-dd1c-42e4-9628-d0a27efcda8a", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "投诉不正确的产品链接", "summary": "如果卖家认为产品对比不正确或链接扭曲了价格指数，可提交投诉。Ozon会在3小时内审核并修正。", "content": "- 在'价格与促销 → 产品价格'页面，点击产品价格。\n- 点击相关图标，选择投诉原因并说明。\n- 点击'发送'。\n- Ozon在3小时内审核并修正信息。若不满意可再次投诉。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/ratings/price-index?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["价格指数", "投诉链接", "纠正"]}
{"rule_id": "f3ef02df-279d-4220-886c-db5aaa9e1282", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "产品交付质量评分计算方式", "summary": "质量评分基于过去30天内客户对订单产品的评分，使用正面评分占比公式计算。", "content": "- 评分来自客户在账户中填写的订单调查，每个订单中的产品分别评分。\n- 评分值：1、2、3为负面，4为中性，5为正面。\n- 计算公式：正面评分占总评分的比例。\n- 示例：如果客户在两个订单中评价了4件产品，则基于2个订单评分计算。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/ratings/csat-blocking?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["metric calculation", "quality rating", "order survey"]}
{"rule_id": "6808f350-5bda-4b9c-a143-5eeaecedf93c", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "Storefront审核流程", "summary": "Storefront提交审核后，Ozon最长3天内完成检查，通过后状态变为“Published”。", "content": "- 提交后进入“On moderation”状态\n- 审核时长不超过3天\n- 审核通过后状态变为“Published”；失败则变为“Moderation failed”需修正", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/personal-account/showcase?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["storefront", "审核", "moderation"]}
{"rule_id": "d7998fbe-68ad-40e7-92aa-6979c0e009d8", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "邀请链接有效期及激活流程", "summary": "发送给员工的邀请链接有效期为24小时，员工需在有效期内点击链接完成注册激活。", "content": "- 邀请链接有效期为24小时\n- 员工需在有效期内点击链接激活账户\n- 激活后状态变为“Active”", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/personal-account/user-management?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["invitation", "link", "activation", "time limit"]}
{"rule_id": "b004dacc-73dc-41b6-b71c-ce98ef425455", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "更改店铺Logo的流程", "summary": "商家可通过后台上传新Logo并提交审核，审核不超过3天，通过后发布，失败则替换为默认Logo。", "content": "- 操作路径：Products → Storefronts → Store design → Storefront details → Logo区域\n- 先移除旧Logo，再点击Select file选择图片，点击Send for moderation提交审核\n- 审核时长：不超过3天\n- 审核状态：\n  - Verified：通过并发布\n  - On moderation：审核中\n  - Moderation failed：未通过，显示需修改内容\n- 未通过时自动替换为默认Logo", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/personal-account/store-name?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["logo", "change process", "moderation"]}
{"rule_id": "c565ec88-3c75-408d-8791-9ad509fba808", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "点数折扣机制：卖家承担折扣，获得点数用于支付佣金", "summary": "Ozon可为卖家产品设置额外折扣，折扣成本由卖家承担，卖家获得与折扣等值的点数，用于抵扣佣金费用。", "content": "- Ozon代表卖家对产品应用额外折扣，折扣成本由卖家承担。\n- 卖家获得的点数等于产品原价与实际售价之间的差值（1点=1合同货币单位）。\n- 点数可用于支付当月最多99%的销售佣金。\n- 若点数不足，剩余佣金从卖家收入中正常扣除；若点数超出，超出部分转为奖金支付。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/accounting/discounts-for-customers/discount-points?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["points", "discount", "commission", "seller_fee"]}
{"rule_id": "49c87a4b-d27e-405b-bfbf-69ed62b23758", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "点数不影响卖家总收益，仅改变结算方式", "summary": "点数机制只改变Ozon与卖家之间的结算方式，卖家的总收益不变。", "content": "- 2024年3月1日前后结算方式不同：之前折扣以货币形式返还，之后以点数形式。\n- 无论何种方式，卖家最终实际收入相同（示例中均为900,000 RUB）。\n- 点数可抵扣佣金，剩余部分仍以货币支付。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/accounting/discounts-for-customers/discount-points?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["points", "settlement", "earnings"]}
{"rule_id": "0e3758a6-f6d5-483a-b1fd-48059d586e5f", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "点数扣除佣金顺序及额度限制", "summary": "点数优先用于支付当月销售佣金，最多可覆盖佣金的99%。", "content": "- 点数按顺序自动扣除：先抵扣点数，再扣除剩余佣金（货币）。\n- 抵扣上限为当月总佣金的99%。\n- 如果点数不足，剩余佣金从卖家收入中正常扣除。\n- 超额点数转为奖金，无需缴纳增值税。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/accounting/discounts-for-customers/discount-points?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["points", "commission", "deduction", "bonus"]}
{"rule_id": "f3ce99a6-833c-40c5-b027-dfba0131c19a", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "产品上架流程", "summary": "上架产品需设置价格、更新库存并等待1-3天审核。审核结果通过颜色标识：绿色可售，黄色有小错误可售但影响排名，红色失败不可售。", "content": "- 开始销售产品前必须完成：设置价格、更新仓库库存、等待审核（通常1-3天）。\n- 产品状态在“产品 → 产品列表”页面查看，颜色含义：\n  - 绿色：通过审核，产品可销售。\n  - 黄色：存在小错误，产品可销售但搜索结果排名较低。\n  - 红色：未通过审核，存在严重错误，无法创建或更新PDP。\n- 子状态解释主状态原因，例如“On sale - Updating the product”表示产品正在审核更新但仍可销售；“Ready for sale - Out of stock”表示缺货不可销售。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/products/upload/created-pdp/status?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["product status", "moderation", "listing process"]}
{"rule_id": "fef8c5f8-09b2-4b0c-85d8-b7250d09dc9b", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "加入促销的方式与促销类型选择", "summary": "卖家需将产品添加到指定的促销类型（如“弹性增量”、“最大增量”等）以参与大促。", "content": "- 在“价格与促销 → Ozon促销”页面，选择促销日历中的促销活动。\n- 可将产品添加到“弹性增量·无限期”、“最大增量”、“最大增量：深度折扣”等促销类型中。\n- 不同促销类型提供不同的提升效果（如搜索提升55%、促销徽章、余额计数器等）。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/promotion/big-promotions/rasprodazha?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["促销", "参与流程", "促销类型"]}
{"rule_id": "dd7a72ec-f964-47a6-8d80-677d42627fc1", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "广告审核流程与时间", "summary": "广告启用或修改后进入审核，通常在工作时间5小时内完成。", "content": "- 审核在启用或更改横幅、视频横幅、推广横幅后进行\n- 审核时间通常为工作日上午9点至下午7点之间，少于5小时\n- 审核不通过时横幅状态变为“Rejected”，广告活动停止\n- 可点击状态旁图标查看拒绝原因，修改后重新提交审核", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/promotion/media-advertising/moderation_of_advertising_materials?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["moderation_process", "rejection", "resubmission"]}
{"rule_id": "126a4a8b-243a-43ca-a03d-09690d782531", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "品牌推广免费试用期", "summary": "品牌推广自动启用后前3天免费，不收取佣金。", "content": "- 如果您销售推广品牌的产品，推广会自动启用。\n- 启用后的前3天免费，不收取佣金。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/promotion/product-promotions/promoted-brands?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["品牌推广", "免费试用期"]}
{"rule_id": "42bd03f0-fc5f-4243-a586-681012db5e15", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "品牌推广的启用与禁用流程", "summary": "品牌推广自动启用，可在“产品→品牌”中禁用；禁用后至少24小时才能重新启用。", "content": "- 如果您销售推广品牌的产品，推广会自动启用。\n- 要禁用推广，前往“产品→品牌”部分，关闭对应品牌的推广。\n- 禁用后，Ozon会停止扣费，并移出推广。\n- 禁用后至少24小时才能再次启用推广。\n- 同样，启用推广后至少24小时才能禁用。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/promotion/product-promotions/promoted-brands?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["品牌推广", "启用", "禁用", "冷却期"]}
{"rule_id": "3a83899c-9193-4340-ba3f-25c976c45c0d", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "库存补货建议操作指南", "summary": "根据产品在FBP仓库的库存天数，Ozon提供不同紧急程度的补货建议，卖家应按照建议优先级操作以避免销售损失。", "content": "- 供应紧急（Supply urgently）：产品库存少于10天，应优先补货。\n- 尽快供应（Supply soon）：库存可维持10-30天，可与其他紧急产品一同补货。\n- 目前足够（Enough for now）：库存超过30天，正常补货即可。\n- 供应到FBP（Supply to FBP）：realFBS日均销量>1件且无FBP库存，建议转为FBP补货。\n- 维持库存（Maintain the stock）：realFBS日均销量<1件，按时补货即可。\n- 不要供应（Do not supply）：过去60天无FBP销售或库存可维持90天以上，不可加入补货单。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/analytics/analytics-and-metrics/dostupnost-tovarov?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["补货策略", "库存管理", "FBP", "realFBS", "供应建议"]}
{"rule_id": "d7cbe1b4-e4d1-46a9-b7da-5c3849892426", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "监控缺货销售额损失与产品可用性指标", "summary": "卖家需关注Lost sales和Product availability两项核心指标，通过定期检查报告和指标控件，及时补货以减少销售损失。", "content": "- Lost sales：因缺货导致的销售额损失，基于日均销售额乘以缺货天数计算。\n- Product availability：产品在FBP和realFBS仓库中有库存的时间百分比，越高损失越少。\n- 系统每日根据过去28天数据更新指标，并考虑在途库存。\n- 若指标显示有Lost sales和待供应产品，应在Product availability详情页查看具体产品。\n- 可通过筛选和下载报告，按建议类型（Supply urgently等）查看推荐补货产品。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/analytics/analytics-and-metrics/dostupnost-tovarov?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["缺货损失", "可用性指标", "销售监控", "绩效"]}
{"rule_id": "0833315e-2e91-4b1a-ac86-3a4a85f91657", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "常见索引错误及解决方案", "summary": "列出商品索引失败的常见原因（创建错误、描述差、字段缺失、无照片、无名称、无价格、缺货超30天）及对应解决方法。", "content": "- **创建商品时出错**：商品因错误未加载。前往“商品→商品列表→错误”检查状态字段，修复错误后重新提交审核。\n- **描述质量差**：商品已上架但未被索引。同样进入“商品→商品列表→错误”查看状态修复。\n- **型号字段为空**：填写型号字段并保存商品。\n- **无照片**：上传照片并保存商品。\n- **无名称**：输入商品名称并保存。\n- **无价格**：输入价格并保存商品。\n- **库存缺货超过30天**：补货，商品详情页将重新索引；若不打算再销售，将商品移入归档，归档商品不会出现在报告中。", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/analytics/fulfillment-reports/indexing-errors?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["索引错误", "解决方案", "缺失字段", "缺货", "listing"]}
{"rule_id": "20320be8-bc29-4ff6-98ae-3ad07bd98d00", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "account_health", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "遭遇欺诈后点击确认并投诉", "summary": "如果已向诈骗者提供账户数据、添加了第三方账户或分享了个人详细信息，请在聊天中点击“确认”按钮并提交投诉。", "content": "- 在客户聊天中点击“确认”按钮，如果：\n  - 向诈骗者提供了账户数据\n  - 向公司资料添加了第三方账户\n  - 分享了个人详细信息\n- 同时提交投诉。", "severity": "critical", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/work-with-customers/customers-chat/chat-safety-rules?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["fraud", "report", "confirm"]}
{"rule_id": "297773b8-25e7-4c8e-a2e0-dfe31c56a82b", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "after_sales", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "负面评价发布前联系客户的流程", "summary": "若客户对产品给出1-3星评价，该评价会延迟96小时发布，商家可在延迟期间通过聊天联系客户解决问题。", "content": "- 当客户评分1-3星时，评价会延迟96小时发布。\n- 商家可在产品→客户评价页面使用发布状态筛选查看延迟发布的评价。\n- 点击延迟评价行或打开评价后点击联系客户，发送消息。\n- 若客户修改评价或评分，更新版会在审核后发布；\n- 若客户无回应或未更改决定，原始评价将在96小时后自动发布；\n- 若客户删除评价，则不会发布。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/work-with-customers/managing-reviews/hide-reviews?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["contact customer", "negative review", "96 hours delay", "review management"]}
{"rule_id": "69cb800b-a5e1-4e7f-b3fa-3dee3c2e98ec", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "after_sales", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "自动选择评论收集活动规则", "summary": "系统自动将评论数不足10或长期无评论的商品加入活动，达到条件后自动移除，卖家无法手动移除。", "content": "- 自动选择包含两类：收集前10条评论（商品评论少于10时加入，达到10条后自动移除）和长期无评论（最近14天无评论的商品加入，收集10条新评论后自动移除）。\n- 卖家无法手动从自动选择活动中移除商品。\n- 自动活动预算无法设置限额，但卖家可查看费用预测，并在达到预算上限后手动停止。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/work-with-customers/points-for-reviews/points-algorithm?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["自动选择", "评论收集", "商品管理"]}
{"rule_id": "3ba395c7-0097-430e-9e30-e37dce6472b5", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "after_sales", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "手动快速评论收集活动规则", "summary": "卖家可自行创建商品列表，设置目标评论数和活动时长，随时可停用，但停用后仍需为活动期间下单并按时留评的订单付费。", "content": "- 卖家创建商品列表，设定目标评论数和活动持续时间。\n- 每条获得的评论按固定费率计费。\n- 卖家可随时禁用活动，禁用后立即移除特殊标签并停止鼓励留评。\n- 如果客户在活动生效期间下单，并在收货后5天内留下评论，即使活动已结束，卖家仍需按活动费率付费。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/work-with-customers/points-for-reviews/points-algorithm?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["手动活动", "评论收集", "停用后费用"]}
{"rule_id": "6e2c4475-8051-4e4c-8ece-a2d7089713c8", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "after_sales", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "查看评论收集报告与计费", "summary": "卖家可通过报告查看活动效果，包括评论内容、评分及每条评论的费用明细。", "content": "- 在商品→快速评论收集的“分析”板块点击“报告”生成报告。\n- 选择报告时间段后生成，最多等待24小时。\n- 报告可用XLS格式下载，包含评论内容、产品评分和每条收取的费用。\n- 若出错，联系支持：促销与特别优惠→促销→营销工具→快速评论收集。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/work-with-customers/points-for-reviews/points-algorithm?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["报告", "分析", "费用明细"]}
{"rule_id": "aa58655e-7b4b-4fc0-807b-4af457fbf68c", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "after_sales", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "自动选择快速评论收集活动", "summary": "可启动自动活动，系统自动将无评论的新产品加入活动，达到10条评论后移除。", "content": "- 在“产品→评论→快速评论收集”页面的“自动选择”部分点击“启动”。\n- 设置活动开始日期，查看产品数量、预期评论数和预算预测。\n- 产品列表每日更新：收到10条评论的产品移出，新无评论产品加入。\n- 活动状态保持“活跃”，无新增产品时14天后停止计费。可随时停止活动。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/work-with-customers/points-for-reviews/start-reviews-for-points?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["expedited_review", "auto_campaign", "product_reviews"]}
{"rule_id": "004af7fc-425e-44bd-ba29-ebcf7b204c20", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "安全保证金缴纳流程", "summary": "卖家在账户的“品牌文档”部分选择品牌，系统自动计算保证金金额，如果余额充足则自动扣款。", "content": "- 在账户 → 商品 → 品牌文档中选择品牌。\n- 系统根据合同币种计算品牌营业额，并与该币种最低/最高保证金比较，确定最终金额。\n- 最终金额按付款当日俄罗斯央行汇率转换为卢布。\n- 若账户余额高于应缴卢布金额，则扣款成功。\n- 保证金有效期为365天，每个流行品牌单独缴纳。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/policies/product-rules-and-documents/documents/originality-confirmation/security-deposit?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["缴纳流程", "自动扣款", "有效期"]}
{"rule_id": "c45c6c48-ed26-4287-b961-2d8eacfc98f7", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "安全保证金退还流程（卖家发起）", "summary": "卖家可随时申请退还剩余保证金，但需同时满足两个条件：21天等待期和缴费后两个月。", "content": "- 卖家可主动要求退还保证金（例如希望禁用“原装”标签时）。\n- 条件一：从申请退款起已过21天等待期（用于检查违规），若在此期间收到违规通知则顺延至仲裁结束。\n- 条件二：保证金缴纳已满两个月。\n- 退还资金将在下一个付款日到账。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/policies/product-rules-and-documents/documents/originality-confirmation/security-deposit?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["保证金退还", "申请条件", "等待期"]}
{"rule_id": "60d97df7-994a-4b62-acf4-30659df4a3eb", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "安全保证金退还流程（Ozon发起）", "summary": "Ozon在特定条件下可主动退还全部或部分保证金。", "content": "- 条件一：保证金缴纳已满两个月。\n- 条件二：自发生以下任一事件起未满21天：\n  - 卖家提供了证明商标独家权利的文件（版权持有人等）。\n  - “原装”服务条款发生变更，Ozon将禁用该服务。\n- 保证金退还后，卖家可重新提交品牌文档并付费激活“原装”标签。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/policies/product-rules-and-documents/documents/originality-confirmation/security-deposit?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["保证金退还", "Ozon发起", "条款变更"]}
{"rule_id": "69c006c7-7191-4f7a-8790-92a42a7a381e", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "恢复促销工具访问的条件", "summary": "若当前周期营业额超过促销成本至少5000卢布，且无债务、期末余额不低于5000卢布，则自动在三天内恢复促销工具访问。", "content": "- 恢复条件：当前周期营业额超过促销成本至少5000卢布。\n- 检查债务为零且“期末余额”至少5000卢布。\n- 满足条件后，在三天内自动恢复访问。\n- 恢复后促销活动处于非活跃状态，需手动重新启动。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/accounting/receiving-payments/finance-management?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["debt", "promotion tools", "restoration", "turnover"]}
{"rule_id": "4e56b7c9-8e00-40e4-89fd-ef98d2baff11", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "多账户下恢复促销工具访问的条件", "summary": "多账户场景下，需所有账户总余额大于0、各账户无债务且当前周期营业额超过广告成本至少5000卢布，才能恢复促销工具访问。", "content": "- 恢复条件：所有账户总余额 > 0。\n- 各债务账户需无债务，即当前周期营业额超过广告成本至少5000卢布。\n- 满足条件后恢复访问。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/accounting/receiving-payments/finance-management?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["multiple accounts", "debt", "restoration", "turnover"]}
{"rule_id": "b0c76d10-26eb-424a-95b8-d1fc4f208802", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "fees", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "合作伙伴银行折扣支付与积分补偿", "summary": "顾客通过合作银行支付获得折扣，合作银行支付部分或全部折扣，剩余部分由Ozon积分补偿。", "content": "- 顾客使用合作银行产品支付时享受绿色价格折扣。\n- 合作银行可能全额或部分返还折扣金额，未覆盖部分由Ozon积分补偿。\n- 示例：产品原价1000卢布，特殊优惠后900卢布，绿色价格再打2%至882卢布，差18卢布；合作银行支付10卢布，Ozon补偿8积分。\n- 积分在月底用于抵扣Ozon推荐费。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/accounting/discounts-for-customers/ozon-card?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["折扣支付", "积分补偿", "合作银行"]}
{"rule_id": "839082ad-a868-4f3c-b41d-48f2f8c87c66", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "在线模板存储期限为14天", "summary": "草稿和已上传模板在更新历史中保存14天，超过期限可能被删除。", "content": "- 在 Update history 部分，草稿和已上传模板均保留 14 天。\n- 14天后文件可能不再可用，需及时处理。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/products/upload/upload-types/online-sheets?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["template", "expiration", "storage"]}
{"rule_id": "445e82e2-7c1b-43bf-b457-52daceda151d", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "创建产品捆绑包的流程（新建时合并）", "summary": "在后台或通过模板创建变体时，需填写相同品牌、型号名称及每件数量，并设置不同货号和捆绑包价格。", "content": "- 在后台点击“创建多个变体”或下载品类模板。\n- 填写型号名称和‘每件商品数量’属性。\n- 确保产品有相同品牌和型号名称，且不同变体使用不同货号和捆绑包价格。\n- 重量和体积按单件填写。\n- 24小时内完成合并并上架。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/products/upload/merging-products/creating-a-bundle?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["bundle_creation", "merge_products", "listing_process"]}
{"rule_id": "63c7cb36-cb87-4c8a-a8b9-9a8810a84857", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "listing", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "合并现有产品页面（PDP）的流程", "summary": "在“产品→产品列表”中选择相同品牌和品类的产品，通过‘合并到PDP’功能合并；若品牌或品类不同，需先选择统一特性。", "content": "- 进入“产品→产品列表”页面，勾选要合并的产品。\n- 点击“操作”并选择“合并到PDP”。\n- 如果产品品牌或品类不同，系统会要求选择统一特性后合并。\n- 合并前确保所有变体状态为“准备合并”；状态为“错误”则需修改特性。\n- 合并后进入审核，24小时内显示在网站上。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/products/upload/merging-products/creating-a-bundle?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["merge_existing_pdp", "listing_process"]}
{"rule_id": "11d56a7d-10c5-4db0-9eea-9fc63e8afbef", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "category_qualification", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "品牌证明文件上传流程", "summary": "卖家需在Products→Brand documents上传文件，文件不超过10MB，审核需5-10个工作日。", "content": "- 前往Products → Brand documents，点击Add document。\n- 填写证明文件详情及有效期（不接受无期限文件）。\n- 上传电子版文件，最大10MB。\n- 点击Add document提交审核，审核通常需5-10个工作日。\n- 可在同一页面跟踪状态，若被拒会显示原因。\n- 审核通过后，品牌产品将可销售，且品牌详情页会在1天内显示销售权利确认。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/policies/product-rules-and-documents/documents/originality-confirmation/brand?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["上传流程", "审核时间", "文件大小"]}
{"rule_id": "75570839-6472-4415-bbc3-1fa14327e300", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "退货在途超过14天的争议处理", "summary": "客户怀疑产品丢失或卖家未确认收货，发起争议，Ozon联系物流并做出决定。", "content": "- 退货在途超过14天时客户可发起争议\n- Ozon联系物流公司并核查\n- 根据信息决定：确认卖家收到则批准退款；客户未寄出则拒绝；仍在途则标记为运输中", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/fulfillment/rfbs/refunds/deviation?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["dispute", "transit_delay", "14_days"]}
