{"rule_id": "353634ea-d883-41e4-9b38-6f0a469dd7c2", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "更改单个产品的出价", "summary": "仅适用于“平均每次点击费用”策略的活动，用户可修改单个产品的出价，新出价在3小时内参与竞价。", "content": "- 进入“推广 → 按点击付费”部分，打开目标活动。\n- 在“您的出价”列中为指定产品更改数值。\n- 如要批量设置，选中多个产品后点击“设置出价”。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/promotion/product-promotions/pay-per-click/edit-and-pause?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["rate", "bid", "pay-per-click"]}
{"rule_id": "08160c14-556c-47b8-8f97-f085463181c7", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "向广告活动添加产品", "summary": "用户可在现有活动中添加产品；若活动使用“目标支出”策略，新添加的产品默认目标支出为15%。", "content": "- 进入“推广 → 按点击付费”部分，打开目标活动。\n- 点击“添加产品”。\n- 选择产品并再次点击“添加产品”。\n- 注意：若使用“目标支出”策略，默认设为15%目标支出，可后续修改。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/promotion/product-promotions/pay-per-click/edit-and-pause?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["add products", "campaign management", "pay-per-click"]}
{"rule_id": "07918e52-935e-408c-9a18-205c13c7c78b", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "归档和还原广告活动", "summary": "用户可手动归档活动；连续90天不活跃的活动会被自动归档。可在“归档”选项卡查看并还原。", "content": "- 进入“推广 → 按点击付费”部分的“归档”选项卡，查看已归档或自动归档的活动（90天未活跃）。\n- 要还原活动：点击活动旁的“更多” → “从归档恢复”。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/promotion/product-promotions/pay-per-click/edit-and-pause?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["archive campaign", "restore", "pay-per-click"]}
{"rule_id": "8b3f9412-8a63-4ae6-91f4-7d19e721f7b7", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "advertising", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "创建手动按点击付费广告活动步骤", "summary": "在促销模块的按点击付费板块中，通过指定名称、添加产品、选择出价策略和投放位置来创建手动广告活动。", "content": "- 进入促销→按点击付费板块，点击“创建活动”→手动。\n- 指定活动名称并点击“添加产品”。\n- 产品可通过SKU、货号或名称搜索，也可按类别、品牌、仓库和价格筛选，或从其他活动未使用的产品中选择，或启用列表模式批量输入货号。\n- 选择出价管理策略：目标支出、进入TOP、自动策略或平均每次点击费用。\n- 指定推广位置：搜索（搜索结果和目录）、搜索和推荐（搜索结果、购物车、商品详情页和付费订单页）。\n- 设置每周预算：基于每个产品2000卢布，均匀分布7天。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/promotion/product-promotions/pay-per-click/launch-promotion?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["广告活动创建", "手动模式", "按点击付费"]}
{"rule_id": "ca2b61fb-56c3-4115-ae45-365214a2e3bd", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "部分补偿操作流程", "summary": "卖家在realFBS模式下可向客户提出部分退款，客户接受后获得退款并保留商品，减少退货和运费。", "content": "- 客户提交退货请求并说明原因。\n- 请求显示在后台：物流 → RealFBS和FBP退货 → 新建。\n- 卖家选择请求，点击“部分退款”，输入退款金额。\n- 系统通知客户，客户有3天时间决定。\n- 若客户接受，卖家支付指定金额，请求状态变为“已部分补偿”，并体现在现金流报告中。\n- 若客户拒绝或超时，卖家收到邮件通知，需在3天内决定后续处理。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/fulfillment/rfbs/refunds/partial-refunds?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["部分补偿", "realFBS", "退款流程"]}
{"rule_id": "92001e25-f26c-45ec-b0e2-f1a00f147a93", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "returns_refunds", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "客户拒绝或超时后卖家的后续选择", "summary": "客户拒绝或未在3天内确认部分补偿时，卖家可再次提出更高补偿（最多两次）、全额退款、或要求退货等。", "content": "- 可再次提出部分补偿（同一退货请求最多两次）。\n- 可全额退款并让客户保留商品。\n- 可要求客户将商品退回至退货提供商仓库（仅限商品价值超过1500卢布）。\n- 一旦提出部分补偿，可能无法再拒绝退款请求。\n- 建议联系客户确认是否遗漏通知。", "severity": "info", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/fulfillment/rfbs/refunds/partial-refunds?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["后续处理", "卖家选择"]}
{"rule_id": "2de59e1b-94e7-4742-8472-8f8e054cb9e2", "platform": "ozon", "site": "GLOBAL", "original_language": "en", "rule_domain": "logistics_fulfillment", "product_category": [], "rule_type": "process", "title": "仓库拒收请求的处理流程", "summary": "当请求状态变为'Needs to be edited'时，表示仓库因错误拒收，需要查看错误并修正后重新提交请求。30天内未修改的请求将被自动删除。", "content": "- 仓库拒绝请求后，状态变为'Needs to be edited'\n- 在请求草稿中打开'Errors'选项卡\n- 下载错误列表\n- 修正错误后点击'Create request'\n- 注意：30天内未修改的请求会被自动删除", "severity": "warning", "source_type": "official_help_center", "source_url": "https://global-help.ozon.com/en/fulfillment/fbp/supplies/supply-work/application-cancelled?region=CHN", "version": "2026.06.18-r1", "effective_date": null, "expiry_date": null, "last_verified_at": "2026-06-18", "verification_status": "needs_review", "confidence": "high", "related_rule_ids": [], "tags": ["request status", "warehouse rejection", "needs to be edited"]}
